MISSION
Turn the existing NXBuild clickable demo into a premium SaaS case-study showcase that sells UI/UX prototyping services on Upwork.

The project should not behave like a regular product demo only.
It should behave like a sales asset that demonstrates:
- UX thinking
- information architecture
- user flows
- wireframes
- high-fidelity dashboard UI
- clickable prototype value
- developer handoff readiness

PRIMARY BUSINESS GOAL
Use one polished prototype as a high-conviction portfolio piece that supports multiple package tiers on Upwork without changing the quality bar of the visible demo.

TARGET OUTCOME
The prototype should make a client believe:
1. The designer can structure a SaaS product from idea to prototype.
2. The designer understands flows, not just screens.
3. The designer can deliver premium dashboard UI and realistic interactions.
4. The same person can package the work into different paid service tiers.

